         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Botanical and Zoological Garden, Melbourne ¶ 25th September 1861 ¶ My esteemed Doctor, ¶  ¶ I have the honour of sending you herewith the first copy of a bill of exchange of an amount of £7/17/- for t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">61.09.25b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To August Petermann</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Wellcome Institute for the History of Medicine, London, Western manuscripts, 56583.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS black-edged. For a published version of this letter, see Voigt (1996), p. 33. See also F. Kupferberg to M, 25 September 1861 (in this edition as 61-09-25c).</p>
               </note>Melbourne im bot. u. zool. Garten,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">am 25. Sept. 1861</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Mein hochgeehrter Herr Doctor.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe die Ehre Ihnen hierbei die prima eines Beitrages von £7.17/- zum Heuglin Fond zu übersenden. Diese Summe ist, wie Sie aus beigefügtem Schreiben ersehen werden, grössenteils vom deutschen Turnverein zusammengebracht nur habe ich £2, von Herrn Dr Landvoigt in Sandhurst gezeichnet, noch hinzugefügt. Die Wechsel von £20. welche ich selbst zu dem schönen Unternehmen beitrug, sowie die prima eines Beitrages von £11 (wovon jetzt die Secunda folgt, sind hoffentlich bei vorheriger Monats-Post richtig bei Ihnen eingetroffen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es soll mir zur besonderen Freude gereichen, auch fernerhin für die Zuschüsse zum Heuglin Fond zu wirken.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Kann ich den wissenschaftl. Anstalten Gothas in irgend einer Weise nützlich sein, so zögern Sie nicht über meine Dienste zu gebieten.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Verehrungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Herrn Dr. Petermann</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gotha<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation by Petermann: 'Erh. 21. Nov. 1861' [Received 21 November 1861].</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c &amp;c &amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanical and Zoological Garden, Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">25th September 1861</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My esteemed Doctor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour of sending you herewith the first copy of a bill of exchange of an amount of £7/17/- for the Heuglin Fund. This sum, as you will see from the enclosed letter,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See J. Sprinckhorn to M, 23 September 1861.</p>
               </note> has largely been collected by the German “Turnverein”,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Gymnastics Club.</p>
               </note> but I have added £2, subscribed by Dr Landvoigt of Sandhurst.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Now Bendigo, Vic.</p>
               </note> The bills of exchange for £20. which I have myself contributed to this laudable enterprise, and the first copy of a bill of exchange for the amount of <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>£11 (of which the second follows herewith) will I trust have reached you safely by last month’s mail.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It will give me the greatest pleasure to continue to collect contributions for the Heuglin Fund.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If I can be of use in any way to the scientific institutions of Gotha, please do not hesitate to command my services.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours respectfully,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr. Petermann</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gotha</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c &amp;c &amp;c</p>
         </div>
      </body>
